    <title>Accurate inference of crowdsourcing properties when using efficient allocation strategies</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/02/08/2020-02-08-accurate/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/02/08/2020-02-08-accurate/</id>
